Package: bscui
Type: Package
Title: Build SVG custom user interface
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        "Patrice", "Godard",
        role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
        email = "patrice.godard@gmail.com"
    )
    )
Description: Produce interactive SVG figures with selectable and clickable user
   interface elements. These figures can be integrated in markdown documents or
   in shiny applications reacting to events triggered on them.
   Features also include moving, zoom in/out and export in SVG or PNG formats.
URL:
   https://patzaw.github.io/bscui/,
   https://github.com/patzaw/bscui/
BugReports: https://github.com/patzaw/bscui/issues
Depends:
   R (>= 4.1)
Import:
   htmlwidgets,
   xml2
Suggests:
   knitr,
   rmarkdown,
   dplyr,
   readr,
   stringr,
   glue,
   shiny,
   DT
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
